    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (((tmp + 0.96 * v1 + 0.35) - 0.43) / (wp.exp(tmp + 0.36) * wp.exp(v2 + 0.55)))
    v1 = wp.abs(wp.cos(wp.exp(v0 + 0.84)))
    v2 = wp.sin(0.96)
    tmp = (v0 / ((v0 + 0.38 + v2 + 0.15) - (tmp + 0.09 + tmp + 0.72)))
